      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--white)">Our <span>Services</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin:0 auto;">End-to-end travel solutions for agents and holidaymakers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">🏨</div>
        <h4>Hotel Booking</h4>
        <p>Curated hotels across all budgets with special agent rates and instant confirmation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">🚌</div>
        <h4>Transfers</h4>
        <p>Private and SIC transfers with professional drivers. Airport pickups, city tours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">🎭</div>
        <h4>Sightseeing</h4>
        <p>Guided tours, theme parks, cultural experiences — fully customizable itineraries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-icon">🎟</div>
        <h4>Ticket Booking</h4>
